OL,3,CDIY e-bike with battery taped to frame
OL,4,Cseized by police
OL,6,FPolice have seized a DIY e-bike which
OL,7,Fthey've described as 'extremely
OL,8,Fdangerous'.
OL,10,FThe driver had taped a battery to the
OL,11,Fframe, which powered the rear wheel
OL,12,Fand was controlled by a throttle.
OL,14,FStaffordshire Police said "Bikes like
OL,15,Fthis are illegal to ride on the road,
OL,16,Fand the driver has found out the hard
OL,17,Fway. Six points on his licence plus a
OL,18,Ffine.
