OL,3,CDIY e-bike with battery taped to frame
OL,4,Cseized by police
OL,6,F"This type of modification can be
OL,7,Fextremely dangerous as it was
OL,8,Funregulated and had the same power as
OL,9,Fa regular motorbike."
OL,11,FThe bike was stopped on West Way in
OL,12,FStafford on Thursday 8 August and
OL,13,Fseized under the Road Traffic Act 1988
OL,14,Ffor driving without third-party
OL,15,Finsurance and driving otherwise than
OL,16,Fin accordance with a licence.
